reviewText:
The Kinsey Sicks group has been around for many decades, helping others and sending the message that its right to be openly gay.  Unfortunately, I found this documentary too focus on their personal issues. I was expecting to see how the group makes a different in the gay community, I did not want to see they did not get "diva treatment" while performing in Las Vegas.  Just like the Vegas promoter mentioned on the film, many entertainers will go starving (if necessary) to get the opportunity to perform in a big venue like the Hilton in Las Vegas.
The problem between cast members totally turn me down, I was a big fun of the group until now. How can you be sending the message to others to love each other, when in fact, the are struggling to love themselves.
There were many scenes that I feel were completely unnecessary. Why we needed to know how an HIV positive man its screwing young boys in Puerto Vallarta. Yikes!

I think this drag queens are worse than the diva drag queens from Rupaul Drag Race, totally lost on their own ego. The essence and roots of this group are way gone. I will never be able to see this infamous group with the level of respect I had for them again.
Interesting but not for a movie. Should have been listed under documentary.
Good music vie but i want to see more dark Vader.
Couldn't make it passed the first 10 minutes of brutal self promotion...this is a group of people that love themselves even more than I imagine their fans do.
Entertaining and intriguing peek into what makes the Kinsey Sicks run. Talent, beauty and schtik need hard work and business acumen to keep the dolls up front.
I think this is a fabulous documentary! You get to see how the Kinsey Sicks started, what they do on tour, and you also get to know the boys behind the girls!

It is about the Dragapella Beautyshop Quartet as they prepare for Vegas. The beginning of this flick was far better than the end. This is because the flick seemed to drag on and on at the end. However, you should get a laugh or two from this flick.
